		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷骗骗花喷出3个电磁球，落地造成<span color="#ffacff">33%</span><span>伤害，持续接触造成</span><span color="#ffacff">10%</span><span>伤害，其会作为障碍，一直抵挡弹射物攻击直至其消失。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="511" width="423" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷骗骗花旋转花瓣，造成3段<span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷骗骗花初始附属3枚「雷之实」，每施放一次爆发就消耗1个「雷之实」。当「雷之实」全部消耗后，其会停止攻击，钻地并重新装填3个「雷之实」。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷骗骗花消耗一个雷之实进行蓄力，并附属<span textDecoration="underline">薄雷胄甲</span><span>，破坏即眩晕。蓄力完成后发射激光，直接命中造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害，激光可能产生连续爆炸，每下造成</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">常发生在<span color="#e599ff">拔假植物、突然刷出</span><span>时施放。<br/>雷骗骗花从地下钻出，对地面上单位造成</span><span color="#ffacff">300%</span><span>伤害。即将钻出时地面会有对应特效。一般闪现不会造成伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/电气骗骗花.assets/Image_13.png')" x="720" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
